,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"喺哥倫比亞大學就係讀咗啲咁嘅垃圾返黎"},{"pid":"2e348cf40e1fd88fe21c5266c37fdbf564a9a695","tid":844562,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"所以點解你係「前官員」囉"},{"pid":"65c30f363d14a69a93a2d95bd208c1a7f636f721","tid":844562,"uid":36004,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"dfd245e8e600eecec56eec853f84295f73b1e966","tid":844562,"uid":137921,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png&h=2d0825c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97987d95486a1dfbda4ebc17a991132bb9e87aba","tid":844562,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29b99738fb296636da50a299d3c0b7e76832f3ba","tid":844562,"uid":78971,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"你玩得開心咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"最緊要開心"},{"pid":"c8a7e2e6635f90b208e9f321ea06c9677184eddb","tid":844562,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"輸到有斯德哥爾摩症候群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375d0d1201f68123ab5332dd989f6f95cd050017","tid":844562,"uid":105958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"把劍亮左去邊?"},{"pid":"7d034dbcf18cb344345f7174c8e7f654844f7cc0","tid":844562,"uid":56618,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本矛盾是結構性的，當大陸持續在經濟及軍事上趕上美國，雙方勢必有衝突。大陸並不預期美國將不經一戰就放棄主導地位，也<span style=\"color: red;\">早知無論2016是誰當選美國總統</span>，中美關係都不會平靜無波，他們認清自己該做的是：不管美方的壓力，持續因應大陸各項內政問題、讓經濟成長、擴大中國的國際影響力。(聯合報 記者馮克芸)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真d啦<br />\n2016都唔改返啱"},{"pid":"2e7f1021157c5a4a48fbd79347675b4085ebc083","tid":844562,"uid":41270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:14:45.000Z","msg":"你而家講曬出黎，美國唔同中國打貿易戰點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國咪冇得贏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1248cc20d4a4024a0e6beb9c9277c3e1c45b2281","tid":844562,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"美國就係想你認輸<br />\n點知打到你輸晒都仲覺得自己贏<br />\n果然係無得輸嘅贏國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfa761ad47570b436be8e4366f975da8723fe74","tid":844562,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"自High <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caff2bd42b17255918520b93ad066097912726a","tid":844562,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"精神勝利法"}]}